text: Toshio Fukui is a modern pentathlete from Japan. Toshio competed at the 1968 Summer Olympics. He was born on January 2, 1943.Toshio Fukui == References == Category:1943 births Category:Living people Category:Olympians for Japan Category:Japanese modern pentathletes Category:Sportspeople from Shimane Prefecture
